- 'Global GDP ranking' is the ranking of countries based on their GDP per capita on a global scale;
- 'Continent GDP ranking' is the ranking of countries based on their GDP per capita within their respective continents.

sql:
SELECT MAX(gdp_per_capita) AS max_gdp_per_capita
FROM countries
WHERE continent = 'Asia' AND population > (SELECT AVG(population) FROM countries WHERE continent = 'Asia');

SELECT COUNT(country_id) 
FROM countries 
WHERE sovereignty = 'Sovereign State';

