- Financial transactions include both deposits and withdrawals, with deposits contributing positively and withdrawals negatively to the total amount;
- The query orders the results by the adjusted GDP per capita in descending order to identify the most prosperous countries.

sql:
SELECT population
FROM country_capitals
WHERE country_id = 0;

SELECT CAST(REPLACE(population, ',', '') AS REAL) AS total_population
FROM countries
WHERE country_id = 0;

